## Commands

```bash
# Development
bun run dev               # Start API + watch
bun run type-check       # TypeScript only
bun run lint             # Biome lint
bun run format           # Biome format

# CI (same as .github/workflows/ci.yml)
bun run ci               # type-check + boundary-check + tests

# Database
bun drizzle:generate     # Generate migrations from schema
bun drizzle:migrate      # Apply migrations
bun drizzle:seed:dev     # Seed development data

# Build & Deploy
bun run build            # Build for prod
docker build -f deploy/Dockerfile -t api:latest .
# systemd: sudo systemctl restart app
```

